# ===== Regenerable workspace =====
# apktool / jadx output and all built APKs live under work/. Everything here
# is regenerated from:
#   - backup/*.apk (the upstream factory APK; tracked)
#   - overlay/     (our edits, keyed by overlay-manifest.txt; tracked)
#   - make build   (decompiles if needed, applies overlay, repackages).
work/

# Backup APK is intentionally NOT ignored — it is the reproducibility anchor.
# If it grows beyond 100MB and you push to a host with that limit (GitHub),
# move it to git-lfs; locally plain git handles the size fine.

# ===== Signing / secrets =====
*.keystore
*.jks
*.idsig
*.pem
*.p12

# ===== macOS =====
.DS_Store
._*
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# ===== Editors / IDEs =====
.vscode/
.idea/
*.iml
*.swp
*.swo
*~
\#*\#
.\#*

# ===== Misc =====
*.log
tmp/
.claude/
